Located in Plouharnel near Carnac, in the heart of the Bay of Quiberon & close to the Gulf of Morbihan, a small Lodge Hotel with swimming pool "different" & full of charm where the welcome and the service are attentive. Each room or Mini Suite is decorated with care. You can relax by the hotel's outdoor swimming pool (in season) or enjoy our new Balneo / SPA area - Indoor swimming pool 31°- Jacuzzi 35° - Hammam - Solarium - after having enjoyed the Sauna or body treatments. All the beautiful beaches are just a few minutes away by car or by bike. Breakfast is served from 8:00 am to 10:30 am in the living room overlooking the garden with tropical accents or in your room and on the terrace when the weather and temperature allow it.
